			<title class="- topic/title ">
				<ph outputclass="topicnum"
  					class="- topic/ph "
  					props="autonumber">5332.501-2</ph> Unusual Progress Payments</title>
			<conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
				<ol class="- topic/ol ">
					<li outputclass="List 1"
  						class="- topic/li ">
						<p outputclass="List 1"
 							class="- topic/p ">(a)(3)  The contracting officer must submit contractor requests for unusual progress payments through the SCO to <xref href="mailto:usaf.pentagon.saf-aq.mbx.saf-aqc-workflow@mail.mil"
    								scope="external"
    								format="mailto"
    								class="- topic/xref ">
								<u class="+ topic/ph hi-d/u ">SAF/AQC</u>
							</xref> with a recommendation to approve or disapprove the request.  SAF/AQC will forward all requests for unusual progress payments, whether recommended for approval or disapproval, to <xref href="mailto:usaf.pentagon.saf-fm.mbx.saf-fmfc-afafo-accounting-workflow@mail.mil"
    								scope="external"
    								format="mailto"
    								class="- topic/xref ">
								<u class="+ topic/ph hi-d/u ">SAF/FMF</u>
							</xref> with all pertinent data supporting the recommended action for approval and submission to <xref href="mailto:osd.pentagon.ousd-atl.mbx.cpic@mail.mil"
    								scope="external"
    								format="mailto"
    								class="- topic/xref ">
								<u class="+ topic/ph hi-d/u ">OUSD(A</u>
								<u class="+ topic/ph hi-d/u ">&amp;</u>
								<u class="+ topic/ph hi-d/u ">S</u>
								<u class="+ topic/ph hi-d/u ">)/DP</u>
								<u class="+ topic/ph hi-d/u ">C</u>
							</xref>. </p>
